'''3-巯基丙酸'''（'''3-MPA'''）是一种[[有机硫化合物|有机硫化合物]]，化学式为HSCH<sub>2</sub>CH<sub>2</sub>CO<sub>2</sub>H，分子中有[[巯基|巯基]]和[[羧基|羧基]]。它是油状液体，可以[[3-氯丙酸|3-氯丙酸]]为原料，或[[丙烯腈|丙烯腈]]和[[硫脲|硫脲]]为原料制备。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.chemicalbook.com/CAS_107-96-0.htm|title=107-96-0|publisher=ChemicalBook|accessdate=2020-11-14|archive-date=2020-11-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201120070508/https://www.chemicalbook.com/CAS_107-96-0.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>由于巯基的硫对金有亲和力，它被用于制备亲水性的[[金|金]]纳米颗粒。<ref>{{cite journal|title=Catalysis with TiO2/Gold Nanocomposites. Effect of Metal Particle Size on the Fermi Level Equilibration|author1=Subramanian, Vaidyanathan |author2=Wolf, Eduardo E. |author3=Kamat, Prashant V.|journal=Journal of the American Chemical Society|year=2004|volume=126|pages=4943–4950|doi=10.1021/ja0315199}}</ref>

